    <title>搭建Hexo博客笔记</title>
    <link href="https://carotin.github.io/2016/09/26/github-hexo-blog/"/>
    <id>https://carotin.github.io/2016/09/26/github-hexo-blog/</id>
    <published>2016-09-26T04:39:04.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-09-26T08:03:41.139Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="建立本地站点"><a href="#建立本地站点" class="headerlink" title="建立本地站点"></a>建立本地站点</h2><h3 id="环境搭建"><a href="#环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="环境搭建"></a>环境搭建</h3><blockquote>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="external">NodeJs</a></li>
<li><a href="http://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">Git</a></li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-cli -g</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>+<a id="more"></a></p>
<h3 id="配置Hexo"><a href="#配置Hexo" class="headerlink" title="配置Hexo"></a>配置Hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo -v     <span class="comment">#查看是否安装成功</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo init   <span class="comment">#新建一个网站</span></div><div class="line">$ npm install <span class="comment">#安装</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo g      <span class="comment">#生成静态文件</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo s      <span class="comment">#启动服务预览</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="快速开始"><a href="#快速开始" class="headerlink" title="快速开始"></a>快速开始</h2><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My New Post"</span>  <span class="comment">#建立新文章，默认在_posts下，layout="draft"时发布的是草稿</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Released-a-draft"><a href="#Released-a-draft" class="headerlink" title="Released a draft"></a>Released a draft</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo publish &lt;filename&gt;  <span class="comment">#将_drafts下的文件放到_posts下，也就是发布草稿</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo server  <span class="comment">#启动服务预览</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="部署到Github"><a href="#部署到Github" class="headerlink" title="部署到Github"></a>部署到Github</h2><h3 id="修改-config-yml-文件参数"><a href="#修改-config-yml-文件参数" class="headerlink" title="修改 _config.yml 文件参数"></a>修改 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件参数</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">deploy: </div><div class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</div><div class="line">  repo: git@github.com:username/username.github.io.git</div><div class="line">  branch: master</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="安装SSH"><a href="#安装SSH" class="headerlink" title="安装SSH"></a>安装SSH</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"your_email@example.com"</span></div><div class="line">$ ssh -T git@github.com</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="安装-hexo-deployer-git"><a href="#安装-hexo-deployer-git" class="headerlink" title="安装 hexo-deployer-git"></a>安装 hexo-deployer-git</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="安装-hexo-deployer-heroku"><a href="#安装-hexo-deployer-heroku" class="headerlink" title="安装 hexo-deployer-heroku"></a>安装 hexo-deployer-heroku</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-heroku --save</div><div class="line">``` </div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">### Generate static files</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">``` bash</div><div class="line">$ hexo generate  <span class="comment">#生成静态文件</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo deploy  <span class="comment">#部署(发布)到远程服务器</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Hexo-常用命令"><a href="#Hexo-常用命令" class="headerlink" title="Hexo 常用命令"></a>Hexo 常用命令</h2><h3 id="命令简化输入"><a href="#命令简化输入" class="headerlink" title="命令简化输入"></a>命令简化输入</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo n  <span class="comment"># == hexo new</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo p  <span class="comment"># == hexo publish </span></div><div class="line">$ hexo g  <span class="comment"># == hexo generate</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo s  <span class="comment"># == hexo server</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo d  <span class="comment"># == hexo deploy</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="其它命令"><a href="#其它命令" class="headerlink" title="其它命令"></a>其它命令</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo clean    <span class="comment">#清除缓存文件</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo list     <span class="comment">#列出网站资料</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo version  <span class="comment">#显示版本信息</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo --safe   <span class="comment">#在安全模式下，不会载入插件和脚本。</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo --debug  <span class="comment">#调试模式</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo --silent <span class="comment">#隐藏终端信息</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo --draft  <span class="comment">#显示草稿</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="特殊命令"><a href="#特殊命令" class="headerlink" title="特殊命令"></a>特殊命令</h3><p>自定义配置文件的路径<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo --config custom.yml <span class="comment">#自定义配置文件的路径，执行后将不再使用 _config.yml。</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>自定义 CWD<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo --cwd /path/to/cwd <span class="comment">#自定义当前工作目录（Current working directory）的路径。</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>文章参考：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="external">Hexo</a>官方文档</p>
]]></content>
    
